    "description": "<p><em><strong>When you fuse with your spirit</strong></em>, roll <strong>+Sulphur</strong>. On a 7-9 hold 2, on a 10+ hold 3. On a 6- hold 1 but <strong>mark contamination</strong>. Spend a hold to use the spirit&rsquo;s power. Work it out with the GM, but it should be about the level of a spell from Drink Deep: rapid healing, temporary invulnerability, a burst of flight, etc. When all&nbsp;hold is gone the spirit&rsquo;s power is spent, and you can&rsquo;t fuse again until you use Shelter or Rest and Recreation.</p>",
